				\begin{document}$$I_{{{\text{sc}}/G}} = \, \left( {\frac{G}{{ \, G_{0} }}} \right)I_{{{\text{sc}}/G_{0} }} .$$\end{document}

The above model calculates the PV cell photocurrent, which depends on the radiation and the temperature according to equation [20]:Iph=(Icc+Ki(T-298))GG0,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
